item.title: 5 Day - London Itinerary
item.description: Traveling the a place like London can be a bit overwhelming, but no worries, I have you covered. Check out our itinerary and some pointers we learnt along the way, so have a wonderful experience in London, and be able to enjoy as many of the attractions as time for you permits. Below is the itinerary we followed, feel free to modify as needed.
